text: Ðes synd þa landgemaera to Myceldefer.
Arest <on> Myceldefer, andlang mearc weges on þone sand pytte, þonan anlang þara ealdena dala, þonan oster þone beorh <þæt> lið betweol þan twan langan beorgan.
Þonan to Worðigsaetena mearc, andlang Wordihaema mearc on þone hlinc bufan Friþelinga dic, of þan hlinc on þat suðmyste gat, andlang dic on þat ealden fyrd gat.
Of þam fyrdgat on ða hocedan dic, of þaere hocedan dic on Dennerdes treow, of þam treow on weg gelaetan, norðrihtis to Waddanyge swa innan þone broc to Miceldefer.
